Name: The Dictatress
About the game: This is a simplistic dungeon crawler top-down looter shooter controlled with the keyboard only. It's characteristic for it's pixelated raytracing graphics rendered on the CPU. You play the role of a soldier enforcing the law and protecting yourself in the chaotic underground of your country. While leveling up, collecting gear and a civil war breaks out, you prepare for a final decision to make. I won't tell you now, but you will find out in the end. we got shooting, looting and chatting to NPCs!
